
The cloud is fueling the rise of disruptive technologies, transforming established business models and opening up unprecedented growth opportunities for businesses to innovate and provide substantial value to their customer base.

Several case studies exemplify how the adoption of emerging technologies on the cloud is generating significant value for a global audience:

Utilizing the cloud-based Internet of Things to combat the poaching of endangered rhinos in South Africa.

Leveraging Artificial Intelligence on the cloud to deliver distinctive digital experiences to millions of fans worldwide, as demonstrated by the United States Tennis Association.

Applying Blockchain on the cloud to assist farmers in minimizing waste through enhanced traceability and transparency in the food supply chain.

Employing data analytics to drive predictive maintenance solutions for a city's infrastructure, as exemplified by KONE.
